Day 48: Deploy Pods in Kubernetes Cluster

Date: October 16, 2025
Overview
Created my first Kubernetes pods and understood the basics of K8s.
Key Concepts Learned

Pod architecture
YAML manifests
kubectl command basics
Pod lifecycle

Commands Used
bashkubectl run nginx --image=nginx
kubectl get pods
kubectl describe pod nginx
kubectl delete pod nginx
yamlapiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: my-pod
spec:
  containers:
  - name: nginx
    image: nginx:latest
Challenges Faced
Understanding the difference between pods and containers. Pods crashed due to image pull errors!
